headline: Hormel Foods (HRL) Lags Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Hormel (HRL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.33% and 0.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
